---
const stages = [
  { n: '01', title: 'Business Strategy', q: 'What are we trying to achieve?' },
  { n: '02', title: 'Operating Model', q: 'How should the business operate?', active: true },
  { n: '03', title: 'Capabilities', q: 'What creates value?' },
  { n: '04', title: 'Solutions', q: 'How do we enable it?' },
  { n: '05', title: 'Delivery', q: "What's the best way?" },
];
---

<section class="section section--dark framework" id="framework">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head center reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow on-dark" style="justify-content:center">The Framework</p>
      <h2>Every technology decision should trace back to the business.</h2>
      <p class="lead">
        Software isn't your operating model — it's one way of enabling it. The review works back from
        strategy, not forward from tools.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ol class="flow reveal" data-delay="1" aria-label="From business strategy to delivery">
      {stages.map((s) => (
        <li class={`flow__step${s.active ? ' is-active' : ''}`}>
          <span class="flow__n">{s.n}</span>
          <span class="flow__title">{s.title}</span>
          <span class="flow__q">{s.q}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>

    <figure class="framework__pull reveal">
      <blockquote>
        “If we were designing this business from scratch today, how would we want it to operate?”
      </blockquote>
    </figure>

    <div class="framework__split reveal" data-delay="1">
      <div>
        <h3><span class="dot" style="background:var(--teal-bright)"></span>Differentiating</h3>
        <p>The capabilities that set you apart. Often worth designing for your organization specifically.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3><span class="dot" style="background:var(--coral)"></span>Commodity</h3>
        <p>Payroll, accounting, identity, payments. Long since solved — buy, don't rebuild.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .flow {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
    counter-reset: none;
  }
  .flow__step {
    position: relative;
    padding: 1.75rem 1.1rem;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--ink-hair);
    transition: border-color 0.3s var(--ease);
  }
  .flow__step.is-active { border-top-color: var(--teal); }
  .flow__step::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -6px; left: 0;
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ink-hair);
  }
  .flow__step.is-active::before { background: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(44,138,134,0.2); }
  .flow__n {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-on-dark-faint);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .flow__title {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .flow__step.is-active .flow__title { color: var(--teal-bright); }
  .flow__q { display: block; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-on-dark-muted); }

  .framework__pull {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 5.5rem) auto clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  }
  .framework__pull blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--fs-quote);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-on-dark);
  }

  .framework__split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    max-width: 780px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-top: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-hair);
  }
  .framework__split h3 { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .framework__split .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex: none; }
  .framework__split p { color: var(--text-on-dark-muted); font-size: 1rem; }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .flow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .flow__step { border-top: none; border-left: 2px solid var(--ink-hair); padding: 0.9rem 0 0.9rem 1.5rem; }
    .flow__step.is-active { border-left-color: var(--teal); }
    .flow__step::before { top: 0; left: -6px; }
    .framework__split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
